{
  "texts": [
    "On the other hand, if it is asked the same question in Korean, it would give you the similar answer, but only containing 4 catetories of the features of the insect.",
    "Even though this is a simplistic example, it unequivocally demonstrates the disparity in the amount of information accessible when conversing in English compared to when conversing in other languages.",
    "It is widely known that recent language models have improved significantly (Devlin et al. 2018, Brown et al. 2020, Clark et al. 2020).",
    "Recent advancements in language modeling have embraced the approach of training large-scale models on extensive, unannotated corpora using self-supervised learning techniques.",
    "These methods involve predicting masked words and the next sentence in a sequence."
  ]
}